<article id="post-2" class="post-2 page type-page status-publish hentry">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title">Home</h1>
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<div class="fcbkbttn_buttons_block" id="fcbkbttn_left"><div class="fcbkbttn_button">
                            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/" target="_blank">
                                <img src="http://evaristo.co.uk/wp-content/plugins/facebook-button-plugin/images/standard-facebook-ico.png" alt="Fb-Button" />
                            </a>
                        </div><div class="fcbkbttn_like "><fb:like href="http://evaristo.co.uk/" action="like" colorscheme="light" layout="standard"  width="225px" size="small"></fb:like></div></div><p>Welcome to Evaristo&#8217;s web site. Here you will learn everything you will need to be successful in your life.</p>
<p>On this website I will explain how I understand The Law Of Attraction and everything you can do to make it work for you.</p>
<p>I will give you tips on improving your life, some of my ways might not work for you but I am sure half of them will help you to get you were you want go.</p>
<p align="LEFT"><span style="font-size: large;">In the last five year I have been searching about the law of attraction. I have had so many experiences.</span></p>
<p align="LEFT"><span style="font-size: large;">The way I understood how this law worked was by taking a look at my past and by making small experiences, like thinking about a £1 coin and giving all my energy to this thought which resulted in me finding or getting a £1 coin in some way.</span></p>
<p align="LEFT"><span style="font-size: large;">So I will share with you my £1 story. I was sitting on the sofa at home and I thought that today was a good day to test the law of attraction. I give all my energy to the thought of a £1 coin.</span></p>
<p align="LEFT"><span style="font-size: large;">I went for a jog and came back 45 minutes later and nothing happened. I took a shower and got dressed. Someone knocks on the front door, I take 5 to 7 minutes to open the door and when I open there is nobody there. I close the door and thought I saw a coin on the floor, so I open the door again and there was £1 coin just in front of me. I just thanked the universe for showing me that the law of attraction really exists.</span></p>
<p align="LEFT"><span style="font-size: large;">These small experiences make you believe even more.</span></p>
<p align="LEFT"><span style="font-size: large;">If you want know more about the law of attraction I recommend you see <a title="Law Of Attraction Tips" href="http://evaristo.co.uk/law-of-attraction-tips">Law Of Attraction Tips</a>. You will see lots of people, book&#8217;s, website&#8217;s, videos, etc. talking about this law.</span></p>
<p align="LEFT"><span style="font-size: large;">I am talking about the law of attraction because I know everything I have now, I asked for it. &#8220;So if I know I&#8217;m am the creator of my live why don&#8217;t I make my live the way I really want it to be?&#8221; Seems a bit stupid, but unfortunately most people hear about it but just keep saying to themselves &#8220;it is not so easy, but.. but.. but..&#8221; Stop saying to yourself  &#8220;but my partner don&#8217;t let me, but this city is poor, etc., etc.&#8221; Take responsibility of your life, thoughts and actions&#8230;.</span></p>
<p align="LEFT"><span style="font-size: large;">The time you take responsibility for your life, thoughts and actions, you start living the right path. Every time you want to do something it first starts with a thought and then passes to an action. Sometimes we think about doing something and we don&#8217;t take action. To the universe it means we don&#8217;t really want it. Our brains resets every 37 seconds, so I recommend when you have a good thought write it down on a piece of paper for two reasons. Firstly because our minds don&#8217;t stop &#8220;24/7&#8221;, this way we forget some thoughts or dreams, and secondly because when we write it on a piece of paper we give more good energy to this thought. It is a good idea to read it twice a day for 30 days. The law of attraction will do the rest.</span></p>
